{"tid":274754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】金鐘站列車驚現持槍男　反恐特勤隊出動搜捕","createTime":"2017-06-07T14:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T15:04:07.000Z","uid":20933,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aef78359aa18709ce018ae28a1d102275d806722","tid":274754,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T14:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170607/large/1496843784_66b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170607%2Flarge%2F1496843784_66b1.jpg&h=cb9f0883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅衫持搶男驚現港鐵金鐘站列車。<br />\n<br />\n傍晚6時許，有市民在港鐵金鐘站赫見一名懷疑持槍的男子，在港島線月台登上往中環列車，致電報警求助。警方接報後到場調查，反恐特勤隊警員亦出動，正搜捕涉案可疑男子。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，涉案懷疑持槍男子年約30至40歲，身穿紅色運動衫、黑色褲及黑色鞋，揹着一個藍色斜孭袋。現場消息指，疑人登上列車後，坐在座椅上仍緊握疑似手槍物體。警方接報後分別到金鐘站調查，亦到中環站堵截可疑男子。"},{"pid":"d7d9e8f352a48e660f754621ae0ae79567006df8","tid":274754,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T14:11:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170607&amp;guid=56797650&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170607%26guid%3D56797650%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=vLc4vZpLGAOVEDaTVy6HsP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=2522a298\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170607%26guid%3D56797650%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=fdce689d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170607&amp;guid=56797650&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"af58c4cfd6f95c6f705fbf5ed265b42ae23a11a4","tid":274754,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T14:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b2229b77016